2020 V and C without Unemployment

This is the example vignette for function: snw_a4chk_wrk_bisec_vec from the PrjOptiSNW Package. This function solves for the V(states, check) for individuals working. Dense solution. Bisection, most time for the test here taken to genereate the income matrixes. But these can be generated out of the check loops.
